{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a vast, inhospitable alien world, you are the expendable. Cloned from DNA for a single purpose: to test the most devastating, over-the-top, and downright absurd weaponry known to the galaxy. Welcome to NIMRODS, the ultimate survival roguelite shooter where the guns you craft are the legacy you leave. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Beyond Survival</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Experience the innovative roguelite where your previous gun builds aren't just memories\u2014they're your backup! Deploy guns crafted from past runs in drones to assist the next grunt.  Every run is a story, but each gun is a heroic saga. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086430/extras/StorePage_Drone_CutOut.gif?t=1736371516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Boundless Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Embark on a journey through diverse alien biomes, each meticulously molded by a distinct set of enemies and bosses. Every corner is teeming with specialized encounters and valuable resources to discover. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086430/extras/StorePage_Biomes_CutOut.gif?t=1736371516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Assemble the Unthinkable</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Break the game with your creativity. Collect insane weapon parts from airdrops and craft combinations so powerful, so bizarre, they have to be seen to be believed. Create your dream weapon, or a nightmarish contraption that defies all laws of physics and common sense. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086430/extras/StorePage_CrazyGun_CutOut.gif?t=1736371516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bio-Engineer your Evolution</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Delve into unique progression systems where DNA modifications can evolve your future clones. Tailor your abilities and your drone's AI to complement your playstyle, and optimize your upgrade drops for pivotal enhancements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086430/extras/StorePage_UI_CutOut.gif?t=1736371516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Guns Over Glory</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> As the corporate overlords watch from above, you're constantly faced with hordes of relentless aliens. Complete insane missions, stack bodies, and remember: you probably won\u2019t make it, but your guns definitely will. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086430/extras/StorePage_Death_CutOut.gif?t=1736371516\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hive and Seek","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2086430/b55ceddd196dffb54cd3b535c2bc9cb8e9da5761.jpg"},{"name":"Wingman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2086430/db2dc238c5fe25892c371983c5b80310d81cbdcb.jpg"},{"name":"Vandalism","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2086430/30ced06bfe612a1e3a1d987959bfb9bbde3c5430.jpg"},{"name":"Spray & Pray","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2086430/523e5cea74f341ca877107a95f9a5e8845ea7ace.jpg"},{"name":"Bountiful Harvest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2086430/7480482a90ca0066ba0bd66699122398e25c0993.jpg"},{"name":"Incoming!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2086430/8244fa7e9b371aaf914efa91d6fcd94c8e3292ab.jpg"},{"name":"Gang Buster","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcomm